oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: East Main Street located in Jackson, Tennessee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of East Main Street located in Jackson, Tennessee. The Arrington house and the Curtis house can be seen lining the street. There is an unidentified man in an automobile in front of the houses, with people gathered around him.
